              <a href="/services/" class="inline-flex min-h-[40px] items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-[color-mix(in_srgb,var(--nm-fg)_12%,transparent)] px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-[var(--nm-fg)] transition hover:bg-[var(--nm-surface-muted)]">שירותים נוספים</a>
